query:
insert into raabta_user
            (id, display_name, first_name, last_name, email, phone_number, user_role)
        values
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
        on conflict(id) do update set
            display_name = $2,
            first_name = $3,
            last_name = $4,
            email = $5,
            phone_number = $6
